{"article_id":"JR4CvVRBE5E5AayO","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Massachusetts senator endorses presumptive Democratic nominee","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"and puts herself in the frame as possible vice-presidential candidate","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"Senator Elizabeth Warren has declared herself ready to be Hillary Clinton ' s running mate in the US presidential election .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"The Massachusetts senator","depth":11},{"id":4,"text":"- popular among the progressive wing of the Democratic party -","depth":11},{"id":5,"text":"made the declaration","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"shortly after endorsing Clinton ,","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"calling her \" a fighter with guts \"","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"who would keep Donald Trump out the White House .","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"In an interview on MSNBC , Warren was asked by Rachel Maddow :","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"\" If you were asked to be Secretary Clinton ' s running mate ,","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"do you believe","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"you could do it ? \"","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"In another interview with the Boston Globe on Thursday , Warren endorsed Clinton as the party ' s presidential nominee ,","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"saying :","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"\" I ' m ready to jump in this fight","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"and make sure","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"that Hillary Clinton is the next president of the United States","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"and be sure","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"that Donald Trump gets nowhere near the White House . \"","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"According to the Globe","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"she also praised Clinton ' s primary opponent , Bernie Sanders ,","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"that he had run an \" incredible campaign \" .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"Speaking to MSNBC ' s Rachel Maddow on Thursday evening ,","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"Warren said","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"the Sanders campaign had been \" powerfully important \" .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"\" He ran a campaign from the heart ,","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"and he ran a campaign","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"where he took these issues","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"and really thrust them into the spotlight","depth":13},{"id":31,"text":"- issues","depth":14},{"id":32,"text":"that are near and dear to my heart -","depth":14},{"id":33,"text":"and he brought millions of people into the democratic process , \"","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"she said .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"But ,","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"Warren said ,","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"\" Hillary Clinton won .","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"And she won","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"because she ' s a fighter ,","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"she ' s out there ,","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"she ' s tough .","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"And I think","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"this is what we need . \"","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"Warren ' s endorsement came","depth":4},{"id":45,"text":"within hours of President Barack Obama formally giving his endorsement to Clinton ' s candidacy .","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"\" I ' m with her , \"","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"Obama said , in a video","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"recorded on Tuesday .","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"\" I don ' t think","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"there has ever been someone so qualified to hold this office . \"","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"Vice-President Joe Biden also appeared to give his endorsement on Thursday ,","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"referring in a speech to \" ... whoever the next president is","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"-","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"and God willing","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"it will be Hillary Clinton \" .","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"Warren , a favourite of the progressive left","depth":5},{"id":57,"text":"who taught constitutional law at Harvard ,","depth":5},{"id":58,"text":"is seen as a possible running mate","depth":5},{"id":59,"text":"who could help entice back a disaffected left","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"that has been excited by Sanders but ambivalent about Clinton .","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"Warren has been especially fierce recently in her criticism of Donald Trump ,","depth":5},{"id":62,"text":"attacking the presumptive Republican nominee in a searing string of speeches ,","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"setting herself up for a prominent and pugilistic role in the presidential election","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"whether she is on the ticket or not .","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"Earlier on Thursday , at a speech to the American Constitution Society in Washington DC , Warren hit out at Trump as \" just a businessman","depth":6},{"id":66,"text":"who inherited a fortune","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"and kept it rolling along","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"by cheating people \" .","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"She described him as \" a loud , nasty , thin-skinned fraud","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"who ... serves no one but himself \" ,","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"and said","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"his attacks on Gonzalo Curiel , the federal judge","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"presiding over the Trump University suit ,","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"was \" exactly what you would expect from somebody","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"who is a thin-skinned racist bully \" .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":151,"left":77,"right":150,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":77,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":150,"left":130,"right":149,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":118,"right":129,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":118,"left":94,"right":117,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":94,"left":2,"right":93,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":93,"left":86,"right":92,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":86,"left":82,"right":85,"relation":"elaboration","nucl